Package ca.eshopexpress.model.dto

Class OrderDto

java.lang.Object
ca.eshopexpress.model.dto.OrderDto
public class OrderDto extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing an order. This class is used to transfer order-related data between different layers of the application, such as the service and presentation layers. Contains customer information, order financials, delivery estimate, and payment method.
Since:
2025-05-09
